{"tid":2351670,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【牛牛出城膠行】 搵維城界石打卡","createTime":"2021-01-03T12:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T13:41:58.000Z","uid":133806,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d84db568412c0ce968632d35919e48968d86b7e5","tid":2351670,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T12:12:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n本牛前幾日痾痾下屎諗起，今年除咗牛牛之年，原來仲係香港開埠180週年紀念（26/1/1841英軍喺上環水坑口插旗）<br />\n所以就的起心肝走出屯門，搵下堆維多利亞城界石嚟打下咭紀念下<br />\nWhat is 維多利亞城界石: <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B6%AD%E5%A4%9A%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9E%E5%9F%8E%E7%95%8C%E7%A2%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2588%25A9%25E4%25BA%259E%25E5%259F%258E%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%25A2%2591&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0KpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=7cb5a8d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%B6%AD%E5%A4%9A%E5%88%A9%E4%BA%9E%E5%9F%8E%E7%95%8C%E7%A2%91</a><br />\n由堅尼地城行去跑馬地，堅持唔搭車<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉車去堅尼地城，本牛唔想喺西隧食風，所以去上環轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t81UQhC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft81UQhC.jpg&h=6b1db60d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n翻箱倒籠搵番本四環九約陪本牛行<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/handup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WpzCN0W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWpzCN0W.jpg&h=ddfab264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cqyzQcr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcqyzQcr.jpg&h=ba43ccc3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n[09:08] 出發點：堅彌地城臨時遊樂場（第1個界石）<br />\n根據維基資料，舊石俾市政局移咗入去個球場，原本應該喺而家西寧閣個位置<br />\n但個場而家封撚咗，唯有喺鐵絲網出面影入去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜嘢介紹都冇，孤零零咁棟喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fzBaou6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfzBaou6.jpg&h=357289ef&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【同場加映】東華痘局，後面係公廁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WWtcBW5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWWtcBW5.jpg&h=ccaa0825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有吉席街同堅尼地城海傍past and now<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2icBS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2icBS4.jpg&h=2445975e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7yh5cr4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7yh5cr4.jpg&h=34a5d8cf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n跟住就向第二個界石進發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b3e281a191369fc3df380735cf8d0297d77ac36","tid":2351670,"uid":64345,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T12:18:43.000Z","msg":"仆佢個街，咁重要既野政府一啲介紹都無，仲學咩人保育"},{"pid":"7de6c54aff753dc7cbc94c172e46930fdb614975","tid":2351670,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T12:21:21.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"3514c26f37c9532030c1e754cf916d233a1cec31","tid":2351670,"uid":133806,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T12:43:14.000Z","msg":"第二個界石位於薄扶林道近士美菲路<br />\n由於士美菲路最後嗰段係隧道<br />\n人定牛都唔入得，所以改行蒲飛路<br />\n<br />\n本牛冇轆又5.5噸咁重，所以OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（字好靚）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N0YzQkF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN0YzQkF.jpg&h=02a8a809&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nSmithfield<br />\n香港其中一個冇英文尾綴嘅道路<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A3%AB%E7%BE%8E%E8%8F%B2%E8%B7%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%258F%25B2%25E8%25B7%25AF&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0KpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=48c75a0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A3%AB%E7%BE%8E%E8%8F%B2%E8%B7%AF</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sTVKs8J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsTVKs8J.jpg&h=1c669c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第2個界石：薄扶林道近薄扶林道遊樂場<br />\n由山腳行到上嚟真係攞命，上氣唔接下氣，戴著個仆街口罩加個更字<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個界石相信係最唔起眼嘅一個，又冇介紹，棟喺路邊食塵，話時話隔離舊嘢乜傢伙嚟？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UuZCN9G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUuZCN9G.jpg&h=e9929952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f6uLcC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff6uLcC4.jpg&h=3acee24f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n算，折返原路，向第3個界石進發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n英國巴士，配中資廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TdJ0LY0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTdJ0LY0.jpg&h=88d71765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nXGU嘅勢力範圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tpw9Ejn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTpw9Ejn.jpg&h=a6a7e46f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住上去克頓道<br />\n歇下先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/imEjg7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FimEjg7G.jpg&h=7e62092b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個原本係咩屋呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xe62eUY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXe62eUY.jpg&h=9c404ae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第3個界石：克頓道<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eJhtatw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeJhtatw.jpg&h=8f48fc88&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唔知係咪位處西半山上山頂嘅行山要道，所以今次就整晒牌介紹，可惜冇乜人留意<br />\n下次行過駐足下都好呀<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uP3j1AW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuP3j1AW.jpg&h=f20f7054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再向第4個界石進發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa68ab327ca4b87f41a70ff1a97b0a443c495b5","tid":2351670,"uid":133806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b3e281a191369fc3df380735cf8d0297d77ac36","tid":2351670,"uid":64345,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T12:18:43.000Z","msg":"仆佢個街，咁重要既野政府一啲介紹都無，仲學咩人保育"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T12:45:33.000Z","msg":"佢哋一時一樣<br />\n有啲寫兩隻字，有啲有塊牌，有啲乜都冇"},{"pid":"31e9fbcefa30a27db794413f7d690d4f9661ecfc","tid":2351670,"uid":136299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T14:33:36.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd00ffcc3121e21337089bac540842c6696d48e","tid":2351670,"uid":142763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:20:27.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"9ce854f6e9ae82d998e22fcf9bb9ad54ad4f0841","tid":2351670,"uid":301498,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T19:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59484447db6bd2481a00f036cb27b318ada98768","tid":2351670,"uid":133806,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T13:13:26.000Z","msg":"搵完第3個界石打完咭之後，本來可以行回頭路，再沿著干德道向東走去舊山頂道嘅<br />\n但本牛見到天氣唔錯，所以就決定一於向山頂進發，食埋個飯再落山搵界石<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZ0yCCs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZ0yCCs.jpg&h=4f1e4bab&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n途中就去咗松林廢堡休息一下先（肥牛少做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n其實香港地有好多戰堡遺跡，如果邊位巴絲打得閒有興趣都可以行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/spdkhCL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FspdkhCL.jpg&h=7af8b42d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yK8gApw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyK8gApw.jpg&h=07472256&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJcQEZy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJcQEZy.jpg&h=3f6bb963&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【同途加映】玩個滄海桑田大對照<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QEVCjUk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQEVCjUk.jpg&h=a07510e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nXCX4ni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnXCX4ni.jpg&h=feec10e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0XcEygL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0XcEygL.jpg&h=195e8ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順便同個舊郵筒打下咭先<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VFkiOSg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVFkiOSg.jpg&h=1b069202&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLunch time <br />\n自相殘殺<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rGwBAwo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrGwBAwo.jpg&h=acc6ec03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca06616d9f6203d98e85af1db4fbbcb0b65553e4","tid":2351670,"uid":118675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T13:33:38.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0d42bc2f1b3059ea50f8592ec19070e3a480b9fb","tid":2351670,"uid":210398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:20:24.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會唔會去埋馬己仙峽道睇消失咗嗰舊嘅痕跡?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5a3462b5659a1af04a513b6c3937410edd2acd","tid":2351670,"uid":133806,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:33:56.000Z","msg":"第4個界石：舊山頂道近地利根德里<br />\n舊山頂道係舊時山頂班達官貴人其中一個出入維城嘅主要通道，不過人哋嗰陣係坐山兜坐轎，本牛當然係自己碌落山啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（條路好很斜呀）<br />\n呢個界石都係無任何介紹<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dw2M6a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDw2M6a7.jpg&h=8e1f7761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FcmicST.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFcmicST.jpg&h=62fb44a8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住向第5個界石進發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24ebd31103e48830714962fae5298a95480841f","tid":2351670,"uid":133806,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0d42bc2f1b3059ea50f8592ec19070e3a480b9fb","tid":2351670,"uid":210398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:20:24.000Z","msg":"樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會唔會去埋馬己仙峽道睇消失咗嗰舊嘅痕跡?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T14:50:21.000Z","msg":"問得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係有嘅<br />\n第5個界石【消失的界石】<br />\n我本四環九約書入面其實只有記載6個界石<br />\n但上網查過下資料其實有7個<br />\n而嗰一個消失的界石位於馬己仙峽道17號對落，15號隔離<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDGx1P2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDGx1P2.jpg&h=0bc93003&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n根據wiki同蘋果，個界石喺07年被發現移走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20070819/N2NNWSH7T2UZ7VQJ7FDUAEFRXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20070819%2FN2NNWSH7T2UZ7VQJ7FDUAEFRXQ%2F&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0KpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=c413e064\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20070819%2FN2NNWSH7T2UZ7VQJ7FDUAEFRXQ%2F&h=1d4fe1ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20070819/N2NNWSH7T2UZ7VQJ7FDUAEFRXQ/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nKvVZDs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnKvVZDs.jpg&h=1c57a1f3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n13年過去，隔離座樓重修埋，幅牆都生埋樹根，個界石都係杳無音訊"},{"pid":"0cbe2a8b37dc3d7165f4803286da30a055741921","tid":2351670,"uid":318164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:02:50.000Z","msg":"滾回火星"},{"pid":"5f45d0e958683fa26dd2754c4f2c83456f5e5520","tid":2351670,"uid":136299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6bc51df731175aef93e8f86d62f9e9c7c1bca5","tid":2351670,"uid":145021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"無嗱？"}]}